(Notes:) Tj
T*
(- This endpoint is still an observed/local network view, not global consensus truth.) Tj
T*
(- sample_limit is bounded server-side and intended for dashboard/reporting use.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Node/admin operations) Tj
T*
(- POST /network/switch) Tj
T*
(- set active network preference \(mainnet|testnet|regnet\)) Tj
T*
(- requires admin permission + sensitive approval token) Tj
T*
(- rejects while full/miner/wallet nodes are running \(unless overridden\)) Tj
T*
(- GET /nodes/active) Tj
T*
(- returns active process snapshot by role) Tj
T*
(- GET /storage/root) Tj
T*
(- returns effective storage-root info and persisted storage-path config) Tj
T*
(- POST /storage/root) Tj
T*
(- move/set block storage root; requires nodes stopped + admin approval token) Tj
T*
(- GET /emission/status) Tj
T*
(- reads emission tracker record \(emission_state.json\)) Tj
T*
(- GET /burn/status) Tj
T*
(- reads burn tracker record \(burn_state.json\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Send idempotency \(duplicate-payment protection\)) Tj
T*
(- POST /tx/send now requires a client-provided intent_id \(idempotency key\).) Tj
T*
(- The node persists send intents in a local SQLite database:) Tj
T*
(- default path: logs/api/send_intents.sqlite3) Tj
T*
(- override path: ATHO_SEND_INTENTS_DB) Tj
T*
(- Intent lifecycle states:) Tj
T*
(- pending ? request accepted, send in progress) Tj
T*
(- broadcast ? transaction\(s\) built and submitted to mempool) Tj
T*
(- confirmed ? previously broadcast tx set later observed as confirmed) Tj
T*
(- failed ? send attempt failed) Tj
T*
(- If the same intent_id is submitted again with the same payload, the API returns the prior) Tj
T*
(saved result \(idempotent_replay=true\) instead of creating new transactions.) Tj
T*
(- Reusing an intent_id with a different payload is rejected.) Tj
T*
(- GET /tx/intent/{intent_id} returns current intent lifecycle status so clients can poll send) Tj
T*
(progress without resubmitting the payment payload.) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
